<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Account Deletion Confirmation</title>
</head>
<body style="margin: 0; padding: 0; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #f4f4f4;">
  <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="background-color: #f4f4f4; padding: 20px;">
    <tr>
      <td align="center">
        <table width="600" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="background-color: #ffffff; border-radius: 8px; overflow: hidden;">
          <tr>
            <td style="background-color: #6B7280; padding: 40px 20px; text-align: center;">
              <h1 style="color: #ffffff; margin: 0; font-size: 28px;">Account Deletion Requested</h1>
            </td>
          </tr>
          
          <tr>
            <td style="padding: 40px 30px;">
              <p style="color: #333333; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">
                Hi {{name}},
              </p>
              
              <p style="color: #333333; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">
                We've received your request to delete your account. We're sorry to see you go!
              </p>
              
              <div style="background-color: #FEF3C7; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; border-left: 4px solid #F59E0B; margin: 20px 0;">
                <p style="color: #92400E; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0;">
                  <strong>⏰ Grace Period:</strong> Your account will be permanently deleted on <strong>{{formatDate deletionDate}}</strong> (30 days from now).
                </p>
              </div>
              
              <p style="color: #333333; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; margin: 30px 0 20px 0;">
                During this grace period:
              </p>
              
              <ul style="color: #333333; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8; margin: 0 0 30px 0; padding-left: 20px;">
                <li>Your account is deactivated and you cannot log in</li>
                <li>Your data is preserved and can be restored</li>
                <li>You can cancel the deletion request at any time</li>
              </ul>
              
              <p style="color: #333333; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; margin: 30px 0 20px 0;">
                Changed your mind? You can restore your account:
              </p>
              
              <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="margin: 30px 0;">
                <tr>
                  <td align="center">
                    <a href="{{restoreUrl}}" style="display: inline-block; padding: 14px 40px; background-color: #059669; color: #ffffff; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 6px; font-size: 16px; font-weight: bold;">
                      Restore My Account
                    </a>
                  </td>
                </tr>
              </table>
              
              <p style="color: #666666; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6; margin: 30px 0 0 0;">
                If you have any questions or concerns, please contact our support team.
              </p>
            </td>
          </tr>
          
          <tr>
            <td style="background-color: #f9fafb; padding: 20px 30px; text-align: center; border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;">
              <p style="color: #9ca3af; font-size: 12px; margin: 0;">
                © {{year}} Auth System. All rights reserved.
              </p>
            </td>
          </tr>
        </table>
      </td>
    </tr>
  </table>
</body>
</html>
